e.\n\n**Tips:**\n\n* For a spicier curry, add a pinch of cayenne pepper or chili flakes to the pot with the spices.\n*  If you prefer a thicker curry sauce, simmer for a few minutes longer to allow the sauce to reduce. \n*  Serve with a side of naan bread for a complete meal.\n*  Use other fruits in place of mango, such as pineapple, papaya, or peaches.\n\nEnjoy this flavorful and healthy chicken and mango curry!"
