n with Care:**  Haddock has a delicate flavor, so use seasonings sparingly.\n* **Use dairy-free alternatives:**  If you want a creamy sauce, try using plant-based milks or cream, and use alternatives like nutritional yeast or plant-based cheeses. \n* **Get creative with herbs and spices:**  Fresh herbs and spices can really elevate the flavor of a haddock dish. \n\nEnjoy experimenting with these dairy-free and egg-free haddock recipes!"
